Xcode is the integrated development environment by Apple to devlop for Apple platform - iOS, MacOS, TvOS, iPadOS, WatchOS, VisionOS.

TextEditor - Type code 
Compiler - Convert code 
Debugger System - Fix bugs 
Interface System - Interface design 

